Author: sipapito
Text: I can very much relate to this! I'm in the same boat. While it isn't necessarily the same extent physically visible that you're struggling as maybe some others, it's still absolutely a struggle and your feelings are super valid. I feel the same way sometimes like "ugh I should just get worse or get it together" but things are how they are and I'm working on it but it's still a struggle and I absolutely feel ya!
